(11, 72, '', '<p><strong>Highly recommended as:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Safe and sound and punctual with our professional driver</li>\r\n	<li>Safe and sound and comfortable with our qualified cars</li>\r\n	<li>No worry with heavy luggage after a long journey</li>\r\n	<li>No long queue to check in flight and get through passport control area at Vietnam airport for departure, reduced exposure to COVID virus;</li>\r\n	<li>Stress-free right from your hotel to the waiting room at Vietnam airport for flight home.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/departure-assistance#cartransfer\">Departure Airport Transfer</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/departure-assistance#vipdepart\">VIP Departure Assistance</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"background-color:#3498db\">1</span> Departure Airport Transfer</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you haven&rsquo;t had someone arrange the car to take you to the Vietnam airport for departure, don&rsquo;t take the risk of taking a taxi as you can be late for the flight in certain cases. For 100% certainty, use our Departure Airport Transfer. We will get over the traffic in a safe and smooth manner to make sure that you will arrive at the airport on time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the departure date that you inform us, our English-speaking driver will pick you up at your hotel lobby or a defined address in good time (2 hours prior to your departure time for domestic flight or 3 hours for international flight) and take you to the terminal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Little not: Before you go, just check out the COVID test requirements of your destination. In case a Covist test negative result certificate is required, you should visit those&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/vietnam-covid-test/\">health establishments for COVID test in Vietnam</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Departure Airport Transfer Fees (US$/pax)</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Number of travelers</th>\r\n			<th>1 pax</th>\r\n			<th>2 pax</th>\r\n			<th>3+ pax</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Hanoi City</td>\r\n			<td>$22</td>\r\n			<td>$11.5</td>\r\n			<td>$9</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ho Chi Minh City</td>\r\n			<td>$20</td>\r\n			<td>$10.5</td>\r\n			<td>$8</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Those fees are applied for pickup at the city center in Hanoi and Da Nang, and Districts 1 &amp; 3 in Ho Chi Minh City. Picking up at other areas is subject to extra charge.</p>\r\n'),
(12, 72, '', '<h2><span style=\"background-color:#3498db\">2</span> VIP Departure Assistance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You wish to keep heavy packages and follow the long lines to complete departure procedures at Vietnam airport which may take up to 1 hour during the rush hours or you wish to complete those procedures without keeping your luggage and staying in the lines?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the latter is preferred, use our VIP DEPARTURE service as:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our staff will meet you in front of the departure terminal.</li>\r\n	<li>He will assist you with luggage, checking in the flight and getting boarding pass for you.</li>\r\n	<li>He will then guide you through Immigration (exit) Counter quickly, also to the security check.</li>\r\n	<li>You will then just be in waiting room for your departure flight. Now, it&rsquo;s time to head home.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>VIP Departure Assistance Fees (US$/pax)</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Number of travelers</th>\r\n			<th>1 - 2 pax</th>\r\n			<th>3 -4 pax</th>\r\n			<th>5+ pax</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fee (USD/pax)</td>\r\n			<td>$70</td>\r\n			<td>$69</td>\r\n			<td>$67</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n'),
