(29, 83, '', '<blockquote>\r\n<p>There is a common, and short, checklist of what you need in order to apply for a Vietnam visa. This list applies for all passport-holders whose countries do not have visa exemption agreement with Vietnam. If you apply for special visa type (other than the tourist visa), additional documents may be required.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>This is a list of the mandatory documents required for a Vietnam visitor visa (tourist visa):</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Passport requirements:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Passports must have at least 06 months of validity remaining and at least one blank page for the visa sticker. Temporary passports may not be accepted.</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Photos:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Two passport sized photos (4x6 cm and must be recently taken with no glass-wear)</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Application form:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>M3 entry/exit form&nbsp;(for visa on arrival)</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Stamping fee:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Pay by cash upon arrival (for visa on arrival) - $25 USD for single entry and $50 USD for multiple entry</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Approval letter:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>This is required if you want to obtain the visa on arrival at Vietnam&#39;s airport.</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Passport bio page scan:&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>This is required if you apply for an e-visa.</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Credit/debit cards:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>For online payment for e-visa fees.</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Proof of onward travel:</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>In case you are exempt from entry visa requirements.</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Check Vietnam visa requirements by nationality:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Or select your nationality in the list below to check whether you need a visa for Vietnam or not!</p>\r\n'),
(31, 85, '', '<p>This post will let you know how much you need to pay when applying for a Vietnam visa with us.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How much is Vietnam visa?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Vietnam visa cost may vary depending on the way you opt to apply for your visa to Vietnam, as well as the visa type you wish to obtain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here we will give you an overview of Vietnam visa fee if applying with us.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Vietnam evisa fees</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We support Vietnam evisa service at the following cost:</p>\r\n\r\n<table id=\"wpdtSimpleTable-8\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">Processing time</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\">Fee (USD/pax)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1 - 2 pax</td>\r\n			<td>3 - 4 pax</td>\r\n			<td>From 5 pax</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>3 - 5 working days</td>\r\n			<td>50</td>\r\n			<td>49</td>\r\n			<td>48</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>More details</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\">☎ +84946583583</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Note: This fee covers the Government fee (US $25) and our service fee.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Citizens of the following countries can get supported with our evisa service</p>\r\n\r\n<table id=\"wpdtSimpleTable-17\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Andorra</td>\r\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/guide/greece/\" rel=\"\" target=\"_self\">Greece</a></td>\r\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/guide/palau/\" rel=\"\" target=\"_self\">Palau</a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/guide/argentina/\" rel=\"\" target=\"_self\">Argentina</a></td>\r\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/guide/hungary/\" rel=\"\" target=\"_self\">Hungary</a></td>\r\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/guide/panama/\" rel=\"\" target=\"_self\">Panama</a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><a href=\"https://www.vietnam-visa.com/guide/armenia