m-visa-requirements\">Visa Requirements</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-tourist\">Tourist Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-business-visa\">Bussiness Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-embassy-consulate-worldwide\">Vietnam Embassy</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-immigration-blacklist\">Immigration Blacklist</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-exemption\">Visa Exemption</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/tin-tuc\">Visa Blogs</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'Expert consultation.\r\nFree Initial Assessment.\r\n24/7 support.\r\nTransparency in procedure and fees.\r\nTimely delivery is guaranteed.', 'By using this site and making a booking with urgentvietnamvisa.com, you acknowledge that you have read and accepted these Terms and Conditions:\r\n\r\n1. We are a private/commercial website offering expedited e-visa services for an agreed-upon fee. We are not affiliated with any government website.\r\n\r\n2. Please ensure that you double-check the information you provide for your e-visa application, including names, passport numbers, dates of arrival and departure, and ports of entry and exit on the official/government website. We are not responsible for any errors or mistakes made during the e-visa application process.\r\n\r\n3. The fee paid on our website is for the expedited e-visa processing service only. You will also need to pay a $25 USD fee for the e-visa when you apply on the official/government website. (This is for expedited e-visa service. For a new e-visa application, The e-visa fee of $25 USD is already included)\r\n\r\n4. The estimated visa delivery time provided is based on our last 30-day on-time rate and is subject to various factors beyond our control. While we strive to provide accurate estimates, we cannot 100% guarantee the exact delivery time of your visa. Delays may occur due to unforeseen circumstances or additional document requirements. If possible, it is advise that you not to book your flight before receiving your visa!\r\n\r\n5. The e-visa application on our website is for tourism purposes only. If you want a business visa or other type of visa, please do not proceed.\r\n\r\nCancellations and Refunds:\r\n\r\n6. The time displayed on our website is based on the local time in Vietnam (GMT +7). Please ensure that you enter the arrival date using local Vietnam time.\r\n\r\n7. Our expedited e-visa processing fee is non-refundable. Please ensure that you understand the process before proceeding with payment.\r\n\r\n8. For more information, please check out our full terms and conditions at https://urgentvisatovietnam.com/terms-of-use');

