(47, 'Why use Urgent Visa To Vietnam', 'With more than 13 years of hands-on experience, we stand as industry-leading specialists in emergency visa assistance. Our paramount objective is to ensure that no customer misses their flight to Vietnam due to visa-related constraints.', '<p><strong>Hassle-free</strong>: 100% online application</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Convenience</strong>: Apply for all air travelers to Vietnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fastest</strong>: 1-hour for Urgent Vietnam visa request.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cheapest</strong>: Low service fees, no hidden charges</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>More accessible</strong>: Best choice for those living far from Vietnam Embassies</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Since 2010, we have always guaranteed:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Expert Consultation</li>\r\n	<li>Timely Delivery</li>\r\n	<li>Support 24/7</li>\r\n	<li>Complete confidentiality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'passeport-vietnam.jpg', '2022-07-25 17:07:00', '2023-08-03 15:08:15', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'urgent visa to vietnam', 'Why UrgentVisaToVietnam.Com', 'UrgentVisaToVietnam.Com is a website that offers commercial services for obtaining visas for Vietnam. We especially focus on urgent visa service by being able to provide electronic visas within 1-2 hours.', 'why-urgent-visa-to-vietnam', 1),
(49, 'Vietnam Embassy & Consulate worldwide', 'The conventional approach to obtaining a legitimate visa for Vietnam is to reach out to the nearest Vietnam Embassy/ Vietnam  Consulate. This method is particularly advantageous for individuals in proximity to the embassy/ consulate\'s office.', '<p>The conventional approach to obtaining a legitimate visa for Vietnam is to reach out to the nearest Vietnam Embassy/Consulate. This method is particularly advantageous for individuals in proximity to the embassy/consulate&#39;s office.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The overall prerequisites for obtaining a visa through the Vietnam embassy.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Individuals who intend to request a visa for Vietnam at the embassy/consulate must ensure that:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Their passport is valid for at least 06 months following the date of entry into Vietnam;</li>\r\n	<li>Their passport has at least 2 blank pages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>The necessary paperwork for obtaining a visa from the Vietnam embassy.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The essential documents needed for obtaining a visa at a Vietnam embassy/consulate may differ based on the specific embassy/consulate where you plan to submit your application. However, at a minimum, the following documents are typically mandatory:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Original passport</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\r\n	<li>Meeting the requirements above</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. An application form</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\r\n	<li>Which is printed out from the website of the embassy with which you are applying for the visa, completed, and glued with your photo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Sponsor letter from a Vietnam-based company</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\r\n	<li>Required for those who are applying for a Vietnam business visa</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>The process for obtaining a Vietnamese visa at the embassy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The protocol for obtaining a visa at the Vietnam embassy/consulate may vary. While some embassies allow submissions via mail and in person, others only permit in-person submissions. Below is the typical procedure for obtaining a Vietnam embassy visa:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Step 1</strong>: Prepare the documents and fees required by the embassy</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Step 2</strong>: Travel to the embassy to submit the application documents, pay for the visa fee and also get an arrangement note for visa processing, and then travel back home and wait</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Step 3</strong>: Travel to the embassy again to get the visa and passport</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Important Note:</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>To get a visa for Vietnam in this way, you should be aware that:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The visa documents and procedure vary depending on the embassy. So, to save your time and cost, you should call or email them for details before visiting the embassy;</li>\r\n	<li>The application form should be downloaded on the website of the embassy/taken right to the front desk of the embassy as it may not be the same for all embassies/consulates;</li>\r\n	<li>The Vietnam visa fee also varies depending on the embassy;</li>\r\n	<li>You get the visa stamped on your passport before your trip to Vietnam.</li>\r\n	<li>If you are flying to Vietnam and have no time to follow the procedure to get a visa for Vietnam at the embassy, you can consider applying online from us&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://urgentvisatovietnam.com/step-1\">Urgent Visa To Vietnam</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>VIETNAM EMBASSIES WORLDWIDE</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>(*) To obtain information regarding Vietnam embassies/consulates in foreign nations, including their addresses, phone numbers, and email addresses, please select the relevant country from the options below:</p>\r\n', NULL, '2023-03-28 10:03:26', '2023-04-12 10:04:00', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'Vietnam embassy, Vietnam consulate', 'Vietnam Embassy & Consulate worldwide', 'The conventional approach to obtaining a legitimate visa for Vietnam is to reach out to the nearest Vietnam Embassy/ Vietnam  Consulate. This method is particularly advantageous for individuals in proximity to the embassy/ consulate\'s office.', 'vietnam-embassy-consulate-worldwide', 1),
(50, 'Vietnam Visa Guide', 'Welcome to our comprehensive and up-to-date guide for visas to Vietnam! We\'ve got you covered with all the essential information you need, including visa requirements, visa on arrival, e-visa, visa extension, visa renewal, visa fees, and processing time', '<blockquote>\r\n<p>Welcome to our comprehensive and up-to-date guide for visas to Vietnam! We&#39;ve got you covered with all the essential information you need, including visa requirements, visa on arrival, e-visa, visa extension, visa renewal, visa fees, and processing time. Whether you&#39;re planning a short trip or a long stay, our guide will provide you with the necessary details to navigate the Vietnam visa process with ease.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-requirements\"><strong>Check if you need a visa for Vietnam</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first crucial step for every trip to Vietnam is to take care of your Vietnam visa in advance. By doing so, you can save both time and money during the visa application process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"/vietnam-emergency-visa\"><strong>Visa processing time</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure to check the expected waiting time for receiving the letter of approval for Visa on Arrival, both under normal processing and urgent processing. This will help you plan your travel arrangements accordingly and avoid any last-minute visa-related issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"/how-to-apply-for-vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><strong>Vietnam visa on arrival &ndash; the most convenient way to get a visa for Vietnam</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&#39;s explore Visa on Arrival and its essential aspects:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Legitimacy: Visa on Arrival is a legitimate and convenient way to obtain a visa for Vietnam. It is authorized by the Vietnam Immigration Department.</li>\r\n	<li>Eligibility: Visa on Arrival is available for citizens of various countries traveling to Vietnam by air. However, certain nationalities may not be eligible.</li>\r\n	<li>Applicable Airports: Visa on Arrival is applicable at eight major international airports in Vietnam, including Hanoi, Ho Chi Minh City, Da Nang, and more.</li>\r\n	<li>Application Process: To apply for Visa on Arrival, you need to complete an online application on a reputable agency&#39;s website or through the official Vietnam Immigration Department&#39;s website.</li>\r\n	<li>Required Documents: Generally, you&#39;ll need your passport, a passport-sized photo, and a visa approval letter obtained through the online application process.</li>\r\n	<li>Fees: The cost of Visa on Arrival includes a processing fee for the visa approval letter and a separate stamping fee to be paid upon arrival at the airport.</li>\r\n	<li>Arrival Procedure: Upon arriving at the Vietnam airport, head to the Visa on Arrival counter. Present your visa approval letter, passport, photo, and pay the stamping fee to get your visa stamped in your passport.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Following these steps will allow you to smoothly obtain your Visa on Arrival and enter Vietnam hassle-free.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"/all-the-information-you-need-to-know-about-vietnam-visa-extension-and-renewal\"><strong>How to extend and renew your visa in Vietnam</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to our complete and up-to-date guide on extending or renewing your visa while you are in Vietnam. We&#39;ll provide you with all the necessary information and steps to ensure a smooth and successful visa extension or renewal process. Whether you need to prolong your stay or update your visa type, our guide will assist you throughout the entire procedure.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Visa Inforamtion</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/5-common-mistakes-with-vietnam-visa-on-arrival-application\">5 Common Mistakes When Applying for a Visa on Arrival to Vietnam</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/requirements-and-procedures-to-obtain-the-vietnam-5-year-visa-exemption\">5- Year Visa exemption for Overseas Vietnamese or spouse &amp; children of Overseas Vietnamese and Vietnamese citizens</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/download-visa-application-form\">Download Visa Application Form</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/overstay-vietnam-visa\">Overstaying your Vietnam Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-requirements\">Vietnam Visa Requirements</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-types\">Vietnam visa types</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-fees\">Vietnam Visa Fees</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-business-visa\">Vietnam Business Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-tourist\">Vietnam Tourist Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-work-visa-everything-you-need-to-know\">Vietnam Work Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/how-to-apply-for-vietnam-visa-on-arrival\">How to apply for visa on arrival &ndash; Step by step guide</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-evisa-your-ultimate-guide-to-obtaining-an-electronic-visa\">Vietnam E-Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-emergency-visa\">Vietnam Emergency Visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-exemption\">Vietnam Visa Exemption</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/faqs\">Frequently asked questions about Vietnam visa</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/vietnam-visa-photo-instructions\">Vietnam visa photo requirements</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>And last but not least, our <a href=\"/visa-blogs\">travel blog</a>&nbsp;&ndash; Look no further! Our resource has all the valuable information you need, ranging from the best places to explore in Hoi An to maximizing your 3-day stay in Hanoi. Whether you&#39;re seeking cultural attractions, delicious cuisine, or unique experiences, our comprehensive guide will help you make the most of your time in these vibrant cities.</p>\r\n', 'vietnam visa guide.png', '2023-03-28 10:03:49', '2023-08-04 22:08:54', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'Vietnam visa guide', 'Vietnam Visa Guide', 'Welcome to our comprehensive and up-to-date guide for visas to Vietnam! We\'ve got you covered with all the essential information you need, including visa requirements, visa on arrival, e-visa, visa extension, visa renewal, visa fees, and processing time', 'vietnam-visa-guide', 1),
