(3, 'Afghanistan', 1, NULL, NULL, 'Required', 'Vietnam Visa for Afghanistan citizens', '<p><strong>Afghanistan citizens </strong>who hold valid Afghanistan passport is required to obtain a visa before entering Vietnam for tourism, business, or other purposes. Here is all the information you need to know about Vietnam visa&nbsp;for Afghanistan citizens:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Visa Types: Afghanistan citizens can apply for different types of visas including tourist visas, business visas, and transit visas depending on their purpose of visit.</li>\r\n	<li>Visa Requirements: Afghanistan citizens need to submit a visa application along with the required documents which include a passport with at least six months validity, two passport-sized photos, a completed visa application form, and the visa fee.</li>\r\n	<li>Visa Application Process: Vietnam does not have an embassy in Afghanistan, and hence Afghanistan citizens can apply for a Vietnam visa through the embassy in neighboring countries or through an authorized visa agency.</li>\r\n	<li>Visa Validity: The validity of a Vietnam visa varies based on the type of visa and the duration of stay. Tourist &amp; business&nbsp;visas are usually valid for one month or three months.</li>\r\n	<li>Visa Extension: Vietnam visa can be extended once in Vietnam, but the extension process can be lengthy and expensive. It is advisable to apply for a visa with the intended length of stay to avoid any inconvenience.</li>\r\n	<li>Visa Exemption: Afghanistan citizens who have a diplomatic or official passport may be eligible for visa exemption when visiting Vietnam for a short period.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Do Afghanistan Citizens need a visa to Vietnam?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>=&gt; <strong>Yes</strong>. Afghanistan Citizens are <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong>REQUIRED </strong></span>to get a valid visa to enter Vietnam as a tourist or businessmen.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Apply for Vietnam Visa for Afghanistan Citizens?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Afghan