li>Certified business registration</li>\r\n		<li>NA2 &amp; NA16 form&nbsp;which must be completed online <a href=\"https://www.xuatnhapcanh.gov.vn/huong-dan-dvbl-xdnc\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>After that, your sponsor company will submit these documents to the Vietnam Immigration Department which will process the application within 5 &ndash; 7 working days of receipt of full valid documents.</li>\r\n	<li>If the application is approved, your sponsor company will receive a business visa approval letter which allows you to get a business visa for Vietnam.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2: Get a business visa stamp</strong><br />\r\nAt this step, you will get a business visa stamped on your passport at the Vietnam embassy/consulate in your country before your departure for Vietnam.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Vietnam Visa Fees for Monaco&nbsp;Citizens</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Please check the online app for the most accurate pricing information: <a href=\"https://urgentvisatovietnam.com/vietnam-visa-fees\">Vietnam visa fee</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How about urgent Vietnam visa service&nbsp;for Monaco&nbsp;Citizens?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Is it possible to obtain an <a href=\"https://urgentvisatovietnam.com/vietnam-emergency-visa\">emergency Vietnam visa</a> for Monaco&nbsp;citizens? Yes, it is possible to obtain a Vietnam emergency visa for Monaco&nbsp;citizens but the fee will be so high.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any queries or comments regarding the Vietnam visa, kindly contact us at Hotline/WhatsApp: <a href=\"http://wa.me/84904879729?text=Hello%20UrgentVisaToVietnam.Com\"><strong>(+84) 904.879.729</strong></a> or email <a href=\"mailto:sale@urgentvisatovietnam.com\"><strong>sale@urgentvisatovietnam.com</strong></a></p>\r\n', 'Monaco citizens who hold valid Monaco passport is required to obtain a visa before entering Vietnam for tourism, business, or other purposes. Here is all the information you need to know about Vietnam visas for Monaco