(97, 'vn', 'Vietnam Arrival Assistance', 'This service is designed to aid visitors at Vietnam Airport by facilitating visa stamping, visa sticker, and porter service. Our goal is to ensure the highest level of satisfaction for visitors upon their arrival, allowing them to avoid wasting valuable time, particularly after enduring a long flight or for any other personal reasons.', '<p>Do you already have the approval letter and wish to avoid wasting precious time waiting at the Vietnam airport for visa stamping? Why not opt for our Fast-track service to streamline and expedite your visa procedure? The Airport Fast-track service offers the following benefits:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fast Track</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"fast track service\" height=\"561\" src=\"/image/images/fast-track.png\" width=\"890\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>You will be supported:</h3>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Your visa stamp will be sticked without long queue at visa counter.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Number of travelers</th>\r\n			<th>1 pax</th>\r\n			<th>2-3 pax</th>\r\n			<th>4+ pax</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fee (USD/pax)</td>\r\n			<td>$35</td>\r\n			<td>$33</td>\r\n			<td>$30</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>[submit]</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>VIP Fast Track</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"vip fast track service\" height=\"552\" src=\"/image/images/vip-fast-track.png\" width=\"890\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>You will be supported:</h3>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Your visa stamp will be sticked without long queue at visa counter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through the private line at passport control, your immigration stamp will be got quickly</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Number of travelers</th>\r\n			<th>1 pax</th>\r\n			<th>2-3 pax</th>\r\n			<th>4+ pax</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Fee (USD/pax)</td>\r\n			<td>$45</td>\r\n			<td>$43</td>\r\n			<td>$40</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>[submit]</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>It is highly recommended those listed below to use our airport fast track service.</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Those who enter Vietnam the first time;</li>\r\n	<li>Those who need Rush visa. (It will be including with Rush service);</li>\r\n	<li>Those who enter Vietnam with kids;</li>\r\n	<li>Those who travel in a big group;</li>\r\n	<li>Pregnant women;</li>\r\n	<li>Disable people.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Please take a look to understand the airport fast track service run:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Step 1: Choose the airport fast-track service and provide us your exact flight number, departure and arrival time (GMT+7). If your flight is changed, please notify us at least 4 working hours before your departure via email sale@urgentvisatovietnam.com.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 2: Right after landing, our staff will greet you with the welcome-board. In case of early landing, you cannot find our staff, please contact via email sale@urgentvisatovietnam.com.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 3: Our staff will collect your visa approval letter, passport, 2 photos (4x6cm) and entry&amp;exit form, stamping fee and do all the procedures until your visa gets stamped.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 4: Get your passport back with the Vietnam Visa stamped from our staff.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Fast track service refund policy</h3>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Kindly provide us your flight information at least 4 working hours before your flight so that we can arrange our assistant to support you best. Otherwise, there is no refund made even the airport fast-track service cannot be run.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If we already get your flight details but do not offer this service when you arrive, we will refund fully the airport fast-track service you paid.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Arrival Fast Track Service', 'You got the approval letter and you do not want to waste your precious time waiting in Vietnam airport to get visa stamped.', 'vietnam-arrival-assistance', 'fast track service', NULL, 71),
