ion of the sponsor company;</li>\r\n	<li>A Certificate of seal specimen registration or a notice on the publication of information on the sealed specimen of the sponsor company on the national enterprise registration portal;</li>\r\n	<li>Form NA16 &ndash; Registration form for the seal and signature of the legal representative of the sponsor company;</li>\r\n	<li>Form NA2 with Barcode &ndash; Request for pre-clearance of foreigners&rsquo; entry into Vietnam (complete here and print out).</li>\r\n	<li>A photo of the investor&#39;s passport.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Step 2: Submit documents for the Vietnam DT visa approval letter</strong><br />\r\nIn this step, your agent in Vietnam will submit the required documents prepared in step 1 to the office of the Vietnam Immigration Department in Hanoi, Ho Chi Minh City, or Da Nang.</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>After 5 working days, the agent will receive a visa approval letter, which serves as the basis for the foreign investor to obtain the DT visa stamp.</li>\r\n	<li>The agent will then send the scan of the visa approval letter to the investor&#39;s email.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: Your company can also ask a visa agent like Urgentvisatovietnam.com for assistance in these 2 steps. We will submit those documents to the Vietnam Immigration Department on their behalf and then send them the colored scan of your visa approval letter.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Step 3: Obtain the Vietnam DT Visa stamp</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The foreign investor will need to prepare the following documents to obtain the visa stamp for Vietnam entry:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>An original valid passport as prescribed by the law;</li>\r\n	<li>A printout of the Vietnam visa approval letter;</li>\r\n	<li>Two 4*6cm photos on white background</li>\r\n	<li>Vietnamese visa application form.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on the location to pick up the DT visa stamp declared on Form NA2, the investor shall present themselves at the Vietnam Embassy/Consulate General or Vietnam arrival airport for a visa stamp. Then, they can enter Vietnam with a visa.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Get Vietnam Investor DT visa - Hassle-FREE</h2>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>05+ years of experience in Vietnam migration</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 support</li>\r\n	<li>Transparency in procedure and fees</li>\r\n	<li>Timely delivery guaranteed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><em><strong>Disclaimers</strong>: That&#39;s all about how to obtain a DT visa for foreign investors in Vietnam. While we make an effort to ensure that the provided information is correct and up-to-date, there may be changes of which we are unaware.</em></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Everything you need to know about the Vietnam Investor DT visa', 'Vietnam has been emerging as a promising destination for investors in recent years, thanks to its dynamic economy, strategic location, and favorable business climate. For foreign investors who wish to explore the Vietnamese market and seek new investment opportunities, the Investor DT visa is a crucial tool to facilitate their entry and stay in Vietnam', 'everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-vietnam-investor-dt-visa', 'Vietnam investor DT visa', NULL, 92),
